View All
Awards


We believe in doing a good job. For us, awards mean others have recognized our efforts. Here are a few of the recognitions we have recently received:





Herman Miller earns tenth consecutive perfect score in Human Rights Campaign (HRC) Foundation’s 2017 Corporate Equality Index.
 2017
Herman Miller named a 2016 Healthiest 100 Workplace in America.
 2016
Herman Miller earns second WorldatWork Work-Life Seal of Distinction
 2016
Herman Miller achieves twelfth consecutive listing on Dow Jones Sustainability World Index.
 2015







Better World Report









We work for a better world around you.
Learn More








Employees of Herman Miller







Marketing








Engineering








Product Services








Operations








Sales
















You can make a salary making furniture. Or you can make a difference. Or you can work at Herman Miller and make both. Speak up, solve problems, lead others, and be an owner. All while giving back to the community and caring for a better world. Join us and make your mark.
Speak Up
People who speak up and share ideas make for a strong business. Embracing good ideas and sharing the rewards with everyone is one way we stand apart.
Solve Problems
We use design to do that. You don’t have to be a “designer” to make things better—for customers, for the communities we do business in, and for a better world.
Lead
Envision the future and help others reach their potential. Sometimes you’ll lead and other times follow. We believe everyone does both, depending on the problem to be solved.
Own
At Herman Miller everyone can be a shareholder. But more so, you’ll be a stakeholder, because we’re all challenged to design solutions and make decisions that improve our community, our business, and our world.








Why Herman Miller?






            
              Herman Miller


            
              Benefits We Offer


            
              Where We Work


            
              What We Make



At Herman Miller, we design and develop furniture and related services and technologies that improve your environment, whether it’s an office, hospital, school, home, an entire building, or the world at large. In business over 100 years, we continue working hard to design and build a better world around you.
To learn more about Herman Miller and the values that guide us, check out these four videos.




Your health and well-being are important to us. So we give you a range of benefits from healthcare and 401k to an employee stock purchase plan. Benefits are extended to all domestic partners.
We also offer some unique benefits:

$100 rebate on a bike purchase
100% tuition reimbursement
Flexible work arrangements


For a full list of benefits, click here.




Herman Miller is a global company with a presence in more than 100 countries in North America, Asia/Pacific, Europe, Middle East, Africa, and Latin America.
Our world headquarters is in Zeeland, Michigan. Learn more about the area by visiting Hello West Michigan.




Design is a central part of our business. The result is evident in the products we make and services we offer. Each is a reflection of a human-centered design process grounded in research and problem solving.
See the results here.














