Herman Miller (manufacturer)

From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia


					Jump to:					navigation, 					search


Herman Miller, Inc.


Type

Public


Traded as
NASDAQ: MLHR
S&P 400 Component


Industry
Furniture manufacturing
Office and home furnishings retailer


